videos.description: Rutgers QB Arthur Sitkowski is intercepted by Kansas DB Bryce Torneden, who zips into the end zone for a 39-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Jayhawks strike first with pick-6

videos.description: Rutgers LB Deonte Roberts stuffs a Kansas field goal, scoops the ball himself, and chugs it 64-yards to the end zone for a  touchdown.
videos.headline: Rutgers takes blocked field goal to house

videos.description: Jayhawks QB Miles Kendrick lofts a beautiful rainbow pass to WR Jeremiah Booker for the 6-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Kansas QB drops ball perfectly to WR for TD

videos.description: Kansas running back Pooka Williams Jr. busts a 25-yard run, and springboards over a Rutgers defender for a first down.
videos.headline: Jayhawks RB hurdles over defender

videos.description: Rutgers running back Raheem Blackshear drops multiple Kansas defenders with an iron stiff-arm, gaining 23 yards on the play.
videos.headline: Rutgers' RB pounds defenders with stiff-arm

videos.description: Rutgers running back Jonathan Hilliman pounds in a 2-yard touchdown to pull the Scarlet Knights within 10.
videos.headline: Rutgers' RB muscles in goal-line TD

videos.description: Jayhawks running back Khalil Herbert jukes and plants Rutgers' defenders, zooming to the house for a 59-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Kansas RB bursts 59 yards for TD

videos.description: Kansas quarterback Miles Kendrick runs the triple option to perfection and sprints in for the 8-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Jayhawks QB fools defense, sneaks into end zone

videos.description: Kansas running back Pooka Williams Jr. turns on the jets for a 52-yard touchdown run, increasing the Jayhawks' lead over Rutgers.
videos.headline: Pooka Williams Jr. is a blur on 52-yard TD run

videos.description: Running back Keron Thompson breaks free for a 55-yard touchdown burst, the Jayhawks' third 50-plus yard score of the game.
videos.headline: Kansas breaks off another big TD run
